data.description:
This 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home has high ceilings, an attached sunroom and is centered in a great community, school district, & location. 
A perfect investment opportunity for the right investor or a nice find & fixer upper for your family, so bring your skills & imagination! Envision this gem in your portfolio & add your own touch to this lovely home. So hurry & be the first to see this incredible house!
Call for your private showing Today! OPEN HOUSE Coming Soon!
